# GovAssist-RAG — System Architecture

## High-Level Layer Overview

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph PRESENTATION["🖥️ Presentation — Next.js (frontend/)"]
        UI["Chat UI · page.tsx"]
        COMP["Components: button · card\ndialog · textarea · theme-toggle"]
    end

    subgraph CHANNELS["📡 Input Channels"]
        WEB["Web Browser\nHTTP / SSE"]
        WA["WhatsApp\nTwilio Webhook"]
    end

    subgraph API["⚡ API Layer — FastAPI (govassist/api/)"]
        EP_CHAT["POST /chat"]
        EP_STREAM["POST /chat/stream"]
        EP_TTS["POST /tts"]
        EP_SCRAPE["POST /scrape"]
        EP_WA["POST /webhook/twilio"]
        EP_SESS["GET·POST·DELETE /api/sessions"]
        PARSER["_parse_chat_request()\n_parse_twilio_to_chat_request()"]
        STATE_BUILD["_build_state()"]
    end

    subgraph ORCH["🤖 Orchestration — LangGraph (govassist/agents/)"]
        GRAPH["StateGraph · graph.py"]
        MAIN["MainAgent\nPlanner / Router"]
        DOC["DocumentAgent\nOCR + Fields"]
        LLM["LLMAgent\nRefine + Synthesize"]
        RAG["RAGAgent\nVector Search"]
    end

    subgraph RAG_PIPE["🔍 RAG Pipeline (govassist/rag/)"]
        EMBED["EmbeddingService\nBAAI/bge-small-en-v1.5"]
        VSTORE["QdrantManager"]
    end

    subgraph INTEGRATIONS["🔗 Integrations"]
        SARVAM["Sarvam AI\nLLM · STT · TTS · Translate"]
        TWILIO["Twilio Client\nSend · Receive · Media"]
    end

    subgraph STORAGE["🗄️ Storage"]
        SQLITE_S["SQLite schemes.db"]
        SQLITE_C["SQLite chat_history.db"]
        QDRANT["Qdrant Vector DB\nschemes collection"]
        TEMPFS["temp_uploads/"]
        MEMSAVER["MemorySaver\nLangGraph checkpointer"]
    end

    subgraph INGESTION["🕸️ Data Pipeline"]
        SPIDER["Playwright Scraper\nscraper.py"]
        INGEST_S["SQLite insert_scheme()"]
        INGEST_Q["Qdrant refresh_indexes_from_db()"]
    end

    UI --> WEB --> EP_CHAT & EP_STREAM & EP_TTS & EP_SESS
    WA --> EP_WA
    EP_CHAT & EP_STREAM & EP_WA --> PARSER --> STATE_BUILD --> GRAPH
    GRAPH --> MAIN & DOC
    DOC --> MAIN --> LLM --> RAG --> LLM
    RAG --> EMBED --> QDRANT
    RAG --> SQLITE_S
    LLM & DOC & MAIN --> SARVAM
    GRAPH --> MEMSAVER
    EP_SESS --> SQLITE_C
    PARSER --> TEMPFS
    EP_WA --> TWILIO
    EP_SCRAPE --> SPIDER --> INGEST_S --> INGEST_Q
    INGEST_S --> SQLITE_S
    INGEST_Q --> QDRANT
```

---

## LangGraph Agent Routing

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    START(["▶ START"])
    END_NODE(["⏹ END"])

    START -->|"input_type = document"| DOC_AGENT["📄 DocumentAgent\n─────────────────\nPDF → pypdf text\nImage → EasyOCR\nLLM → structured fields\nname · dob · state · income"]
    START -->|"input_type = text / audio"| MAIN_AGENT

    DOC_AGENT -->|always| MAIN_AGENT["🧭 MainAgent — Planner\n──────────────────────────\nSmall talk      → respond\nMeta query      → respond\nScheme keyword  → retrieve\nHas doc context → retrieve\nOut of scope    → respond"]

    MAIN_AGENT -->|"rag_completed=True\nsmall-talk / out-of-scope"| END_NODE
    MAIN_AGENT -->|"route = respond / retrieve"| LLM_AGENT["🧠 LLMAgent — Dual Role\n──────────────────────────────────\nMode A Pre-RAG\n  Normalize query → keywords\n\nMode B Direct Reply\n  Conversational answer\n  uses last 6 messages\n\nMode C Post-RAG Synthesis\n  Build Markdown from schemes\n  _localize_text() if non-English"]

    LLM_AGENT -->|"rag_completed=True\ndirect reply done"| END_NODE
    LLM_AGENT -->|"rag_completed=False\npre-RAG done"| RAG_AGENT["🔍 RAGAgent\n──────────────────────────────\n1. Embed current_query → vector\n2. Qdrant search  top-K = 5\n3. Fallback: SQLite keyword\nsets rag_completed = True"]

    RAG_AGENT -->|"→ post-RAG synthesis"| LLM_AGENT
```

---

## All 5 Input Types

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant SAR as Sarvam AI
    participant G as LangGraph
    participant Q as Qdrant

    Note over U,Q: ① Text only
    U->>API: POST /chat  {query: "schemes for women"}
    API->>SAR: translate_text(auto→en-IN)
    API->>G: invoke(input_type=text)
    G->>G: Main→retrieve
    G->>SAR: LLM refine query
    G->>Q: embed + search
    G->>SAR: LLM synthesize
    G-->>API: final_package → U

    Note over U,Q: ② Speech only
    U->>API: POST /chat  audio.ogg
    API->>SAR: speech_to_text → transcript + lang
    API->>SAR: translate(te-IN→en-IN)
    API->>G: invoke(input_type=audio)
    G->>SAR: refine → RAG → synthesize
    G->>SAR: localize(en-IN→te-IN)
    G-->>API: Telugu answer → U

    Note over U,Q: ③ Document only
    U->>API: POST /chat  aadhaar.jpg
    API->>G: invoke(input_type=document)
    G->>G: DocumentAgent: OCR + field parse
    G->>G: MainAgent: doc context → retrieve
    G->>SAR: refine → RAG → synthesize
    G-->>API: final_package → U

    Note over U,Q: ④ Text + Document
    U->>API: POST /chat  query + file
    API->>SAR: translate query
    API->>G: invoke(input_type=document + raw_query)
    G->>G: DocumentAgent + MainAgent + RAG
    G-->>API: final_package → U

    Note over U,Q: ⑤ WhatsApp (any type)
    U->>API: POST /webhook/twilio
    API-->>U: TwiML 200 ack immediately
    API->>SAR: same parse pipeline
    API->>G: invoke(same state)
    G->>SAR: same agent flow
    API->>SAR: send_proactive_message()
    SAR-->>U: WhatsApp message
```

