## Data Ingestion Pipeline

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    TRIGGER["POST /scrape"] --> BG["subprocess.Popen\nlog streaming back\nto uvicorn"]
    BG --> PLAY["Playwright Chromium"]
    PLAY --> SITES["myscheme.gov.in\n5 categories"]
    SITES --> SCRAPE["scrape_scheme()\nper URL"]
    SCRAPE --> JSON["scheme.json"]
    JSON --> S1["① SQLite\ninsert_scheme()"]
    S1 --> S2["② Qdrant\nBGE embed + upsert"]
    S2 --> DONE["Indexed ✓"]
```

---

## Storage Summary

| Store | Type | Contents | Used by |
|---|---|---|---|
| `schemes.db` | SQLite | Scheme name · category · eligibility · benefits · link | RAGAgent fallback · scraper |
| `chat_history.db` | SQLite | Session ID · title · messages JSON | `/api/sessions` CRUD |
| Qdrant `schemes` | Vector DB | BGE-small embeddings + scheme payloads | RAGAgent primary search |
| `temp_uploads/` | Filesystem | Audio · image · PDF (deleted after request) | DocumentAgent · STT |
| `MemorySaver` | In-memory | LangGraph checkpoint per thread_id = session_id | All agents — conversation memory |

---

## Language Handling Pipeline

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    INPUT["User input\nany language"] --> DETECT["Sarvam translate\nsource_language_code=auto\nnormalize_language_code()"]
    DETECT --> STORE["response_language_code\nstored in AgentState"]
    STORE --> LLM_WRITE["LLM writes answer\nin target language\ne.g. Tamil"]
    LLM_WRITE --> CHECK["_is_mostly_latin()\nDid LLM comply?"]
    CHECK -->|"No — LLM wrote in target lang"| OUT["✅ Use directly"]
    CHECK -->|"Yes — LLM wrote English anyway"| TRANSLATE["_localize_text()\nchunked translation\n1500 chars per chunk\nSarvam mayura:v1"]
    TRANSLATE --> OUT
```
